\is1 Introduction
\ip \bk The igkarangeb sulat of Paul ki Timutiyu\bk*, diye din sulata te Ruma te timpu naprisu sikandin tenged te pegwali rin concerning ki Hisu Kristu. Inhangyu of Paul si Timutiyu egpeendiyeen te kandin te kene pad sikandin eggimatayan. Ne si Timutiyu, diye pad sikandin te Ipisu ka egpanulu te migmalintutuu.
\ip Kayi te seini sulat, intambahan of Paul si Timutiyu eglig‑en eyew egpakaantus sikandin egwali and eggimu te impeyimu te God kandin minsan taliware te me peg-antus and me pegsupak te duma person. Impanpanayan din man‑e si Timutiyu concerning the mareet egkeyingumaan te “keungelan and te ware karuan apulanan” su egpakareet seini te people egpammineg.
\ip Labew te langun, impasuman-suman of Paul si Timutiyu concerning the kandin umul su eyew egkeyimu allegory of Timutiyu ka pegpalintutuu of Paul, ka pegpariralem din, ka peggeyinawa rin, ka pegpabulus din, and ka peg-antus din taliware te me pegbayad-bayad kandin.
